Tim McCoy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_McCoy 0 Timothy John Fitzgerald McCoy (April 10, 1891 – January 29, 1978) was an American actor, military officer, and expert on American Indian life and customs. He was also known Colonel T.J. McCoy. Timothy_John_Fitzgerald_McCoy ( April_10_,_1891 – January_29_,_1978 ) was an_American_actor , military_officer , and expert on American_Indian_life_and_customs .
